title: Neon Blue Icons Pack - ADW GO
creator: DroidAhead

extendedInfo.description: Neon Blue Icons Pack for Launch-X, ADW Launcher EX, Go Launcher EX and LauncherPro.This icons pack includes over 350 HD icons compatible with:* Launch-X (both FREE and Pro versions)* ADW Launcher EX* GO Launcher EX* LauncherPro (both FREE and Plus versions)The icons pack is compatible also with Honeycomb and Ice Cream Sandwich (ICS) devices.** HOW TO USE WITH: ***** LAUNCH-X **** APPLY ICONS PACK *- Open Launch-X- Select an existing widget (or create a new one)- Select 'Appearance Options'- Scroll to the bottom- Click on 'Icons Pack'- Select your desired theme/icons pack* APPLY SINGLE ICON *- Open Launch-X- Select an existing widget- Click on 'Select widget items'- Click on the item you'd like to change the icon- Select 'Custom icon'- Select 'Theme Icons Packs'- Select your desired theme/icons pack- Choose your custom icon*** ADW LAUNCHER **** APPLY ICONS PACK *- Go to your homescreen- Press menu and select 'ADWSettings'- Select 'Themes Preferences'- Under 'Icons' press 'Choose...'- Select your desired theme/icons pack* APPLY SINGLE ICON *- Long-press an item (app/shortcut)- Select 'Edit'- Press the icon button- Choose 'ADWTheme IconPacks'- Select your desired theme/icons pack- Choose your custom icon*** GO LAUNCHER **** APPLY ICONS PACK *- Go to your homescreen- Press menu and select 'Themes'- Press the 'Setting' button- Select 'Icons'- Select 'Theme icon'- Select your desired theme/icons pack* APPLY SINGLE ICON *- Long-press an item (app/shortcut)- Click on 'Replace'- Select 'Theme's icon'- Change the 'Selected theme'- Select your desired theme/icons pack- Choose your custom icon*** LAUNCHERPRO **** APPLY ICONS PACK *- Go to your homescreen- Press menu and select 'Preferences'- Select 'Theme Settings'- Click on 'Icon Pack'- Select your desired theme/icons packTo request new icons simply send us an email to support [at] droidahead [dot] com.
